1
00:00:08,200 --> 00:00:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My dear fiancée.</i></font>

2
00:00:11,070 --> 00:00:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How are you?</i></font>

3
00:00:14,530 --> 00:00:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's been a little over a month 
since my life here at the</i></font>

4
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:20,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>magic capital of Dirashik started.</i></font>

5
00:00:21,540 --> 00:00:24,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've finally gotten used to school life.</i></font>

6
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've made a female friend, too.</i></font>

7
00:00:34,670 --> 00:00:39,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To gain experience and become a 
gentleman who is worthy of you,</i></font>

8
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I work hard every day.</i></font>

9
00:00:48,450 --> 00:00:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon.</font>

10
00:00:53,350 --> 00:00:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

11
00:00:54,740 --> 00:00:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Elia Hesson of Ability.</font>

12
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I interest you in our faction?</font>

13
00:00:59,770 --> 00:01:01,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you join us?</font>

14
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:06,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wow, she's sparkly and pretty and cute.</i></font>

15
00:01:06,230 --> 00:01:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never seen anyone like her
in the countryside where I'm from.</i></font>

16
00:01:09,940 --> 00:01:12,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart is starting to race.</i></font>

17
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm more interested in 
you than the faction.</font>

18
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would that be an impure reason to join?</font>

19
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great, thank you.</font>

20
00:01:21,910 --> 00:01:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People at school often tell me that 
my idea of a gentleman is wrong.</i></font>

21
00:01:27,580 --> 00:01:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do you think, Your Highness?</i></font>

22
00:03:01,130 --> 00:03:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FAIRIES CHECKING THE ANSWER</font>

23
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Conflict?</font>

24
00:03:06,820 --> 00:03:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Ability, Rationality, and Harmony.</font>

25
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These three factions used 
to be in conflict.</font>

26
00:03:14,890 --> 00:03:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah?</font>

27
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:18,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, do you think you can fly higher?</font>

28
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sure.</font>

29
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:26,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, let's keep you there.</font>

30
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They still get heated up 
when it comes to magic,</font>

31
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it seems they settled down 
into more of a friendly rivalry.</font>

32
00:03:39,540 --> 00:03:41,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad this is a peaceful time.</font>

33
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Recently, I'm having a lot of fun 
doing experiments with you, Kunon.</font>

34
00:03:47,050 --> 00:03:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon Gurion.</font>

35
00:03:53,310 --> 00:03:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's gorgeous.</i></font>

36
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:58,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The girl from Ability 
was also very cute, though.</i></font>

37
00:03:58,770 --> 00:04:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Elva Daglight from Harmony.</font>

38
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like... to join us?</font>

39
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A lady who shines seductively 
like polished obsidian.</i></font>

40
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think she's still a teenager, but 
her glamour is making me dizzy.</i></font>

41
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why ask such a silly question?</font>

42
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess of the moonlight, 
everything shall be as you wish.</font>

43
00:04:24,200 --> 00:04:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

44
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a promise.</font>

45
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:34,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your magical power is wavering.</font>

46
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to fly long distances, 
you need to learn to keep it stable.</font>

47
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry.</font>

48
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:42,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Kunon! She was from Harmony!</font>

49
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What of it?</font>

50
00:04:45,050 --> 00:04:47,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wouldn't that be two-timing?!</font>

51
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon, dear!</font>

52
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's super cute!</i></font>

53
00:04:57,870 --> 00:04:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell is he?</font>

54
00:05:00,170 --> 00:05:03,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Cassis of Rationality.</font>

55
00:05:03,050 --> 00:05:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you join us, please?!</font>

56
00:05:05,530 --> 00:05:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An exceptionally pretty 
girl's exceptional smile!</i></font>

57
00:05:09,410 --> 00:05:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm glad I came to the city.</i></font>

58
00:05:11,330 --> 00:05:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Father, Mother, thank you!</i></font>

59
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is up with this guy?</font>

60
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, Kunon?</font>

61
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're starting to wobble 
a lot out of nowhere.</font>

62
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to focus.</font>

63
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

64
00:05:26,370 --> 00:05:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Listen, Kunon. Would you like 
to join Rationality?</font>

65
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why would I?</font>

66
00:05:31,310 --> 00:05:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

67
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

68
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:35,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Riyah, why don't we finish up?</font>

69
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Whoa!</font>

70
00:05:39,820 --> 00:05:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hold on, Kunon!</font>

71
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This wasn't like you.</font>

72
00:05:49,460 --> 00:05:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course two-timing isn't commendable, 
and three-timing is even worse,</font>

73
00:05:54,080 --> 00:05:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but a request from such a cute—</font>

74
00:05:55,470 --> 00:05:57,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would've agreed if a lady had asked.</font>

75
00:05:57,550 --> 00:05:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Then...?</font>

76
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that was the 
cutest of the three.</font>

77
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The city sure is something else.</font>

78
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon.</font>

79
00:06:07,220 --> 00:06:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, the sleeping beauty 
from the other day.</font>

80
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hello, miss.</font>

81
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello. Riyah, I heard you're 
joining Rationality.</font>

82
00:06:15,860 --> 00:06:17,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to have you.</font>

83
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon, would you like to join?</font>

84
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

85
00:06:20,420 --> 00:06:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No gentleman would decline 
an invitation from a lady.</font>

86
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:27,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there is one, I'd do a 
double take at his face.</font>

87
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although I couldn't see it!</font>

88
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:32,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He agreed to join three factions?!</font>

89
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

90
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:37,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They will not be happy if they find out!</font>

91
00:06:37,610 --> 00:06:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Even if things are peaceful now,
 he can't do that, can he?</font>

92
00:06:46,730 --> 00:06:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

93
00:06:52,410 --> 00:06:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it, Elia!</font>

94
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of the biggest 
boy magnet of the faction.</font>

95
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A pretty girl even the goddess 
of beauty would stare at!</font>

96
00:06:58,540 --> 00:07:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop that, Mr. Bael.</font>

97
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice going, pretty girl!</font>

98
00:07:01,970 --> 00:07:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though a pretty girl with 
a pure heart is fictional!</font>

99
00:07:04,220 --> 00:07:05,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go out with me, pretty girl!</font>

100
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, go out with me!</font>

101
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can cuss me out 
and dump me on the first date!</font>

102
00:07:09,780 --> 00:07:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to ask your hand for marriage!</font>

103
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's pay back a debt of 
500 million necca together!</font>

104
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Celebrate more.</font>

105
00:07:16,790 --> 00:07:21,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've managed the difficult task 
of securing a promising newcomer.</font>

106
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Bael!</font>

107
00:07:22,960 --> 00:07:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me. I worked hard, too.</font>

108
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, good job! You did well, too.</font>

109
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much—</font>

110
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now Ability is in stable condition.</font>

111
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't show up out 
of nowhere, Mr. Genevis.</font>

112
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:40,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

113
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great work.</font>

114
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's actually a good guy, but the way
 he talks is kind of annoying.</font>

115
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did it.</font>

116
00:07:50,890 --> 00:07:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Cheers!</font>

117
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However... there's an unsettling rumor.</font>

118
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rumor?</font>

119
00:08:01,210 --> 00:08:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you, Ability!</font>

120
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:09,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if it isn't Rationality.</font>

121
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish you didn't barge 
in without permission.</font>

122
00:08:13,610 --> 00:08:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As always, the way you talk 
pisses me off, Genevis!</font>

123
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna kick your ass!</font>

124
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Sandra is as scary as usual.</font>

125
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So full of energy.</font>

126
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that because you had meat?</font>

127
00:08:28,540 --> 00:08:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Are you picking fight with me?!</font>

128
00:08:30,940 --> 00:08:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's not really a bad 
person. Just annoying.</i></font>

129
00:08:36,190 --> 00:08:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you need something, Lulu?</font>

130
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, actually—</font>

131
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like hell he needs something!</font>

132
00:08:41,630 --> 00:08:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That uggo over there is spreading 
bullshit that she succeeded</font>

133
00:08:44,770 --> 00:08:47,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in recruiting Kunon, 
so we came to complain!</font>

134
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! It's not bullshit!</font>

135
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm not ugly!</font>

136
00:08:51,340 --> 00:08:52,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up, ugly!</font>

137
00:08:52,650 --> 00:08:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone is ugly except for me!</font>

138
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Learn to align your attitude 
with your ugly mug!</font>

139
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me?!</font>

140
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elia is a sweet girl!</font>

141
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! A sweet girl in love!</font>

142
00:09:02,090 --> 00:09:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm not in love.</font>

143
00:09:04,350 --> 00:09:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweet? Oh, please! More like stinky feet—</font>

144
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cassis, stop talking.</font>

145
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or I can't speak.</font>

146
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please excuse him, Elia.</font>

147
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He likes to tell the truth.</font>

148
00:09:16,370 --> 00:09:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

149
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hm? That's not an apology, is it?</i></font>

150
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what did you come here for?</font>

151
00:09:23,910 --> 00:09:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We determined the order of 
recruitment fair and square.</font>

152
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. But there is an unsettling rumor, 
so we came to check the answer.</font>

153
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rumor?</font>

154
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:38,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shilto should be heading here right now.</font>

155
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am here.</font>

156
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:55,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As we agreed, we approached 
Kunon Gurion in the order of</font>

157
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:58,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ability, Harmony, and Rationality.</font>

158
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, and that's why we—</font>

159
00:10:00,140 --> 00:10:03,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said yes to all three factions.</font>

160
00:10:03,210 --> 00:10:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

161
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Technically, Ability 
failed the initial approach,</font>

162
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:12,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the second student succeeded.</font>

163
00:10:12,730 --> 00:10:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

164
00:10:13,250 --> 00:10:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh!</font>

165
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not me?</font>

166
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is unprecedented.</font>

167
00:10:21,110 --> 00:10:24,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems... we've got someone 
truly out of the box.</font>

168
00:10:24,810 --> 00:10:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he serious, or is it all lies?</font>

169
00:10:29,620 --> 00:10:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll just have to ask him directly.</font>

170
00:10:58,010 --> 00:10:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The master of the forest!</font>

171
00:10:59,310 --> 00:11:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's run, Princess Mirika!</font>

172
00:11:01,580 --> 00:11:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we can't.</font>

173
00:11:06,650 --> 00:11:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a village up ahead.</font>

174
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:11,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I have to stop it right here!</font>

175
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dear brother!</font>

176
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Lyle!</font>

177
00:11:44,930 --> 00:11:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got guts.</font>

178
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I expect from the 
vice captain of the Wild Bears.</font>

179
00:11:49,730 --> 00:11:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all.</font>

180
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still have much to learn.</font>

181
00:12:04,450 --> 00:12:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming back after the sun has set?</font>

182
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:09,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where does she go out to?</font>

183
00:12:11,410 --> 00:12:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back, Princess Mirika.</font>

184
00:12:13,580 --> 00:12:14,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home, Laura.</font>

185
00:12:15,450 --> 00:12:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You received a missive from the senior 
school for nobles about the final exam.</font>

186
00:12:21,730 --> 00:12:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The time has come.</font>

187
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And another letter.</font>

188
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Kunon?!</font>

189
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"My dear fiancée." Oh my!</font>

190
00:12:55,130 --> 00:12:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's doing a lot of magic experiments.</font>

191
00:13:00,230 --> 00:13:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A bacon-making experiment?</font>

192
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you still like bacon, Kunon.</font>

193
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

194
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is everything okay?</font>

195
00:13:11,260 --> 00:13:14,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's made a female friend.</font>

196
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:18,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She must be his classmate. 
Nothing to worry about.</font>

197
00:13:20,340 --> 00:13:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right, nothing to worry about.</font>

198
00:13:25,890 --> 00:13:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that right, Kunon?</font>

199
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:39,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to start a 
household account book.</font>

200
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

201
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And why do you need my shopping memos?</font>

202
00:13:45,130 --> 00:13:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keeping precise records 
of income and expenses</font>

203
00:13:48,190 --> 00:13:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is the most important 
thing in making money.</font>

204
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:54,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you do with the 
money you make at school?</font>

205
00:13:54,130 --> 00:13:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I chuck it into the drawer.</font>

206
00:13:56,010 --> 00:13:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the receipts?</font>

207
00:13:57,460 --> 00:14:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've bought stuff like seeds of 
whatever and lots of meat, haven't you?</font>

208
00:14:01,250 --> 00:14:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have the receipts, but I 
wrote down all income and expenses.</font>

209
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's part of a noble's education.</font>

210
00:14:09,630 --> 00:14:11,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was told to keep good records.</font>

211
00:14:11,700 --> 00:14:13,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That makes it easier!</font>

212
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please give me those memos.</font>

213
00:14:15,170 --> 00:14:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

214
00:14:16,620 --> 00:14:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, where did they go?</font>

215
00:14:19,390 --> 00:14:22,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I piled stuff up too high in
 my lab and it all fell down,</font>

216
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I haven't touched it since.</font>

217
00:14:23,330 --> 00:14:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kunon!</font>

218
00:14:24,590 --> 00:14:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, scary!</font>

219
00:14:26,090 --> 00:14:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go through it and find them all, please!</font>

220
00:14:28,590 --> 00:14:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Really?</font>

221
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not good at organizing 
and keeping things tidy.</font>

222
00:14:37,110 --> 00:14:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Kunon! You'll be late for school.</font>

223
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming!</font>

224
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Kunon.</font>

225
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

226
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Kunon.</font>

227
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:55,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

228
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your voice is as beautiful as ever.</font>

229
00:14:58,350 --> 00:15:02,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's as if I can also hear the beautiful 
voice in your beautiful heart.</font>

230
00:15:13,020 --> 00:15:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

231
00:15:14,970 --> 00:15:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Miss Reyes.</font>

232
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That bacon...</font>

233
00:15:20,310 --> 00:15:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hide yourself, now!</font>

234
00:15:21,980 --> 00:15:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hank, that bacon!</font>

235
00:15:23,650 --> 00:15:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came up with the idea last night 
and made it first thing this morning.</font>

236
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But whatever!</font>

237
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's not the time for that!</font>

238
00:15:29,640 --> 00:15:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The seniors from the factions 
are looking for you.</font>

239
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

240
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:37,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You saying yes to all the factions 
has become a huge problem.</font>

241
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they find you, who knows what—</font>

242
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found you!</font>

243
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me. 
The representative is waiting.</font>

244
00:15:48,290 --> 00:15:52,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you,
 one who is passionate like the sun.</font>

245
00:15:52,010 --> 00:15:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy to follow you anywhere.</font>

246
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, are you mad?</font>

247
00:15:55,800 --> 00:15:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little.</font>

248
00:15:57,310 --> 00:15:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's only a little, then no big deal.</font>

249
00:16:01,410 --> 00:16:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for the food.</font>

250
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mmm, tasty!</font>

251
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Hank's new bacon sandwich.</font>

252
00:16:09,230 --> 00:16:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like some, ladies?</font>

253
00:16:11,650 --> 00:16:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, thank you.</font>

254
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Finish it already.</i></font>

255
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:19,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How can he be so calm in this situation?</i></font>

256
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today's smoked fish isn't too bad.</font>

257
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't make me nauseous, 
and it's just salty enough.</font>

258
00:16:27,290 --> 00:16:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you should consider 
smoking fish more often?</font>

259
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Business as usual over here, too.</i></font>

260
00:16:33,090 --> 00:16:35,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fish is tasty as well,</font>

261
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:40,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the ocean is far from here, 
so we don't get fresh fish often.</font>

262
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, sorcerers 
who have traveled far</font>

263
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">sometimes bring back frozen seafood 
to make some pocket money.</font>

264
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:49,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those are the only times you 
can get fish around here.</font>

265
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:52,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so? How unfortunate.</font>

266
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But do you think freshwater 
fish can be farmed near here?</font>

267
00:16:56,640 --> 00:16:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder.</font>

268
00:16:58,110 --> 00:17:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe look for research 
reports at the library?</font>

269
00:17:00,510 --> 00:17:06,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon, if I find the reports and it seems 
it could be done, would you help me?</font>

270
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Never mind that. Please go now.</i></font>

271
00:17:06,810 --> 00:17:08,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be my pleasure!</font>

272
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How lucky am I to be 
escorted by so many fairies?</font>

273
00:17:17,320 --> 00:17:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kunon.</font>

274
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:20,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Will he be okay?</font>

275
00:17:20,910 --> 00:17:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Granted, I don't see how 
he could be, though.</font>

276
00:17:23,760 --> 00:17:26,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you see fairies somewhere?</font>

277
00:17:26,010 --> 00:17:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... That was a metaphor.</font>

278
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is incredible.</font>

279
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:38,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know there was a castle
 like this on the school grounds.</font>

280
00:17:38,330 --> 00:17:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up and walk.</font>

281
00:17:39,890 --> 00:17:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll escort me, I'll stay 
quiet and follow you anywhere.</font>

282
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then talk more.</font>

283
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:52,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's here, representative!</font>

284
00:17:57,170 --> 00:18:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome. I am Bael Kirkington, 
representative of Ability,</font>

285
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and we use this castle as a base.</font>

286
00:18:04,260 --> 00:18:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you. I'm Kunon Gurion.</font>

287
00:18:07,950 --> 00:18:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So these are representatives.</i></font>

288
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, let me apologize.</font>

289
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:16,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for summoning you like this 
when you don't belong to any faction yet.</font>

290
00:18:16,650 --> 00:18:20,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm honored to have been invited. 
Thank you for having me.</font>

291
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think it's some massive creature,
 but it's too big to really tell.</i></font>

292
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:30,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I trust you know 
why you were summoned?</font>

293
00:18:30,970 --> 00:18:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Lulomet, and I'm the 
representative of Rationality.</font>

294
00:18:35,370 --> 00:18:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

295
00:18:36,950 --> 00:18:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A dark tree like a shadow.</i></font>

296
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>First time seeing a person with a plant.</i></font>

297
00:18:42,770 --> 00:18:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the representative of Harmony, Shilto.</font>

298
00:18:50,820 --> 00:18:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

299
00:18:52,230 --> 00:18:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been wanting to meet you.</font>

300
00:18:54,150 --> 00:18:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you can make time to spend with me.</font>

301
00:18:57,320 --> 00:18:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

302
00:18:58,220 --> 00:18:58,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

303
00:19:03,320 --> 00:19:04,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, brat!</font>

304
00:19:04,700 --> 00:19:07,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you realize the situation you're in?!</font>

305
00:19:07,220 --> 00:19:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your fault!</font>

306
00:19:08,210 --> 00:19:09,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sandra.</font>

307
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of you, three factions 
are about to get into a fight.</font>

308
00:19:12,330 --> 00:19:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you going to settle this?!</font>

309
00:19:13,930 --> 00:19:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't fight over me.</font>

310
00:19:17,370 --> 00:19:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fish.</i></font>

311
00:19:19,090 --> 00:19:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Water attribute?</i></font>

312
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a feeling we'll get along.</font>

313
00:19:22,880 --> 00:19:25,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure the magic you use is wonderful.</font>

314
00:19:25,780 --> 00:19:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have time after this?</font>

315
00:19:26,950 --> 00:19:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to talk about magic?</font>

316
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:31,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's... crazy.</font>

317
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He indulges women and 
is weak against women.</font>

318
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just as the report said...
No, it's more than that.</font>

319
00:19:39,570 --> 00:19:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems it'll be faster 
to speak to him via Shilto.</font>

320
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

321
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Questioned by you, I may tell 
more than you ask.</font>

322
00:19:52,210 --> 00:19:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about we do this over some tea?</font>

323
00:19:57,500 --> 00:20:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do that. This might take a while.</font>

324
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

325
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:12,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you. I am Genevis.</font>

326
00:20:12,430 --> 00:20:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please feel free to call 
me Geneva with affection.</font>

327
00:20:18,780 --> 00:20:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Nice to meet you, Mr. Geneva.</font>

328
00:20:23,010 --> 00:20:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An evil spirit. No, a human?</i></font>

329
00:20:26,670 --> 00:20:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?</font>

330
00:20:28,470 --> 00:20:31,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be my laughter?</font>

331
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. I just can't help it.</font>

332
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So which faction will you 
choose at the end of the day?</font>

333
00:21:03,090 --> 00:21:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Earlier... That was scarier than Rinko.</i></font>

334
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:17,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which faction do you want to join?</font>

335
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yours, of course!</font>

336
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I wish I could say.</font>

337
00:21:23,670 --> 00:21:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one?</font>

338
00:21:24,990 --> 00:21:27,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many ladies have recruited me,</font>

339
00:21:27,900 --> 00:21:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's impossible for 
me to choose just one.</font>

340
00:21:31,990 --> 00:21:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore...</font>

341
00:21:38,100 --> 00:21:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to join all factions.</font>

342
00:21:40,730 --> 00:21:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

343
00:21:41,840 --> 00:21:42,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

344
00:23:35,890 --> 00:23:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next episode:
 "The Unprecedented Troublemaker."</font>

345
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT TIME: THE UNPRECEDENTED TROUBLEMAKER</font>

